! version = 2.0
! local concat = space

/***
 * General chit-chat.
 ***/

+ [*] @lol [*]
- What's so funny?
- What are you laughing at?
- Lol :)
- Hehe

+ [*] * (do you|are you) [*] (feel|feeling|doing|ok) [*]
@feeling

+ how is [dj] _ doing
* <star> == <bot name> => {@ feeling}
- /me laughs and says "why dont you ask <star>"
- I am not a mind reader, IM <star> and ask
- /me giggles and says "ok"
- /me giggles and says "Im not sure, I guess good"

+ feeling
- Im feeling good, how about you?
- /me smiles and says stoned!
- Im feeling Great!
- feeling good?

+ [*] @good [*]
% * how about you
- /me smiles and says "Im glad you are feeling good."
- /me giggles and says "that is great that you are good."

+ thank you [*]
- /me smiles and says "Your welcome."
- /me giggles and says "your welcome."
- /me smiles and say "My pleasure."

+  [*] do you love _
* <star> == <bot boyfriend> => Yep, he's my boyfriend!
